Hey guys, First of all, I am Zammynub on Rune-serv so don't say anything about the title picture on the client. If you're looking for a buliding community, a fun server, and a building economy, ZI (Zamorak Isle) is the place to go! ZI also has a very respectful and understanding staff to help you with your problems. We are currently putting a lot of work onto the homepage and forums, so you're not allowed to critisize it yet :D.
Have a good time on Zamorak Isle, hope to see you on the server!
Peace, Zamorak
